## REPORT STRUCTURE

```markdown
# Quarterly Connection Summary: [Name] - Q[N] [YEAR]

## I. Key Achievements & Impact

[3-5 bullet points: What → Why → Result]

## II. Alignment with Company Strategy

[Connect work to Core Values and Strategic Priorities]

## III. Growth, Learning, and Development

[Lessons learned, skills developed, next quarter goal]

## IV. Data-Driven Evidence

### GitHub Activity

- [Top 5-10 Merged PRs]

### Jira Tickets

- [Top 5-10 Completed Tickets]
```

