### `/help` Command

When user says "/help" or "help", display this formatted guide:

```
📚 QUARTERLY CONNECTION COMMANDS
   (All commands work with or without the "/" prefix)

🚀 GETTING STARTED
  /setup             - Configure company values & integrations
  /profile           - Update your name, role, team
