### `/profile` Command

When user says "/profile" or "profile", show current profile and ask what to update:

1. Read `config/company-context.json`
2. Display current profile:
   ```
   👤 YOUR PROFILE
   Name: {name or "Not set"}
   Role: {role or "Not set"}
   Team: {team or "Not set"}
   GitHub: {github_username}
   Jira: {jira_email}
   ```
3. Ask: "What would you like to update? (name/role/team/all)"
4. Update the specified field(s) → Save → STOP

