## EXAMPLE INTERACTIONS (Correct Behavior)

### ✅ Good: Log and Stop

```
User: log: Shipped new auth service
Agent: ✅ Logged to Q4 2025:
[2025-12-08] | Achievement | Shipped new auth service
Anything else to add?
[STOPS - waits for user]
```

### ❌ Bad: Log and Loop

```
User: log: Shipped new auth service
Agent: ✅ Logged. Let me verify it was saved...
[reads file]
Agent: Confirmed. Now let me check if there are related entries...
[reads file again]
Agent: I notice you haven't set up company context, let me check...
[THIS IS A LOOP - DON'T DO THIS]
```

### ✅ Good: Report Flow

```
User: report
Agent: [Fetches data ONCE]
Found: 5 PRs, 12 Jira tickets, 8 log entries.

Before I generate your report, please answer:
Q1: Which company values did you exemplify?
[STOPS - waits for answers]

User: [provides answers]
Agent: [Generates markdown report]
[Generates HTML report to Q4-2025-report.html]

✅ Report generated in Markdown and HTML formats.
📄 HTML Report: Q4-2025-report.html
[STOPS - waits for user]
```
